{"Sid":0,"Did":126872,"Id":"604469","Title":"宜蘭昭應宮前殿螭虎主題木雕","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-15/ba63115f-ebd8-4618-a123-eaa303a942dd/collection/4f3308ca-40af-4e17-8669-1fbf156be237/109-her-pa-2459-202011141322095faf66a9552b80.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-15/ba63115f-ebd8-4618-a123-eaa303a942dd/collection/0ec2ffcf-24a5-4b6f-83c3-9cfcd451853c/109-her-pa-2459-202011141322095faf66a9552b81.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n　　宜蘭昭應宮前殿中港間身堵與腰堵均為螭虎主題之木雕，其圖案構成與前後深度的表現頗具特色，展現出清代道光年間的木雕技藝。\n\n　　螭虎團瓶是臺灣傳統建築常見之主題，螭虎又稱「夔龍」，有趨吉辟邪之意。昭應宮中港間身堵中央的木雕花堵之螭虎團瓶，由4對螭虎所構成，每隻螭虎頭部有清楚可見近似龍頭的鼻子與眼睛，身體由木雕後層往前層似蟠龍狀，組成一個花瓶的形狀，具平安之寓意。此螭虎團瓶的木雕，在瓶身中央與兩側各雕以一隻蝙蝠，四隻蝙蝠有「賜福」之意。\n\n　　昭應宮中港間腰堵的四堵木雕，同樣是螭虎與蝙蝠的組合，畫面主要由兩隻螭虎組成，螭虎的身體盤曲並繞到螭虎頭部的後方，表現出深度感；另一較具特色之處，是螭虎的四爪清楚可見。在此木雕四角則雕以四隻蝙蝠，象徵「賜福」。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY / CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.752819","Keyword_Latitude":"24.757591","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/AD4FE481-AFAC-436E-BBDB-1E829447696C","Original_Identifier":"604469","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","Keywords":"木雕 / 賜福 / 螭虎團瓶 / 夔龍","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2021/01/06 18:24:07","timelines":"","place":"","address":"宜蘭縣宜蘭市中山路3段106號","longitude":"121.752819","latitude":"24.757591","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"無","writer":"蔡明志/ 葉永韶","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-15/ba63115f-ebd8-4618-a123-eaa303a942dd/collectionOpen/6db5ec9b-8c36-4ed0-954e-7f66b312d545/109-her-pa-2459-re-202011141324195faf66a9552b80.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-15/ba63115f-ebd8-4618-a123-eaa303a942dd/collectionOpen/e70eda00-eace-4dfa-91c0-8e65e6459904/109-her-p